/%a initialize dawg %/
<<set $dawg= {

name: "dawg",
dispo: "exploring",
notoriety: 1.2,
bodycount: 0,

health: random(1, 10), maxHealth: 10,
stamina: random(1, 8), maxStamina: 8,
agility: random(1, 6 + 2),
aggression: random(1, 6),
curiosity: random(1, 6),
boldness: random(1, 6),

}>>

<p>you are <<print $dawg.name>>. you have an [[encounter]] while <<print $dawg.dispo>>.</p>

